metadata.name: Half BAYCD: Club Pass
metadata.description:
Half BAYCD is a collection of NFTs that allows you to non-exclusively license BAYC/MAYC/BAKC/Koda assets to a cannabis brand — we are a non-plant touching ancillary company that partners with licensed producers.

By holding a Half BAYCD pass you unlock the ability to license your assets or partner with asset holders to help us build the brand and its story — please visit halfbaycd.com for more information.
